<section id="s-cas-release-401-compatibilitysummary">
  <title>Backward Compatibility Summary</title>
  <para>Protocol changes in CAS since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>There is no backward compatibility with 3.2 because of the port from OGSI
      to WSRF.</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>API changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>None</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>Exception changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>None</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para>Schema changes since GT version 4.0.0</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara>WSDL reflects the port to WSRF from OGSI.</simpara></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
